    m_FontStyle: 0
    m_BestFit: 0
    m_MinSize: 2
    m_MaxSize: 40
    m_Alignment: 6
    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1.1
  m_Text: '<b>Examples 1 and 2</b>

    The first and second example both loop through a simple sequence, successively
    activating items. The first one also deactivates the current item before activating
    the next while the second example keeps all items active until it''s reached the
    end. A typical use case for these examples could be an animation of product labels
    (e.g. key features).


    <b>Example 3</b>

    This example makes use of a more individual set up, being configured the way that
    each item has its own duration parameters instead of global ones. You can build
    your own animation sequence.'
